<p><strong>UPDATE 1: </strong><a href="https://www.gofundme.com/f/support-helens-children-after-her-passing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">A fundraiser has been set up by Marcus Arvan to support Helen&#8217;s children</a>.</p>
